<!-- About Hero Section -->
<section class="about-hero">
    <div class="about-hero-content">
        <h1>Our Story of Elegance</h1>
        <div class="hero-divider"></div>
        <p>For over a decade, we've been crafting exquisite ladies suits that celebrate the timeless elegance of Indian fashion with contemporary flair.</p>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Story Section -->
<section class="story-section" id="story">
    <div class="story-container">
        <div class="story-image">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1594736797933-d0d7e08b5113?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1000&q=80" alt="Our Story">
        </div>
        <div class="story-content">
            <h2>Where Tradition Meets Modernity</h2>
            <p class="story-text">
                Founded in 2010 by designer Priya Sharma, Elegant Stitch began as a small boutique in Mumbai's vibrant fashion district.
                What started as a passion project has blossomed into one of India's most beloved ladies suit brands.
            </p>
            <p class="story-text">
                Our journey began with a simple vision: to create suits that honor traditional craftsmanship while embracing modern design sensibilities.
                Today, we continue this tradition, blending intricate embroidery, luxurious fabrics, and contemporary silhouettes to create pieces that
                make every woman feel confident and beautiful.
            </p>
            <div class="quote">
                <p>"Fashion is not just about clothes, it's about telling a story. At Elegant Stitch, we weave stories of elegance, confidence, and timeless beauty into every stitch."</p>
                <p class="quote-author">- Priya Sharma, Founder & Creative Director</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Values Section -->
<section class="values-section" id="values">
    <div class="section-title">
        <h2>Our Core Values</h2>
        <p>These principles guide everything we do, from design to delivery.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="values-grid">
        <div class="value-card">
            <div class="value-icon">
                <i class="fas fa-gem"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Craftsmanship</h3>
            <p>Every suit is meticulously crafted by skilled artisans who take pride in their traditional techniques and attention to detail.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="value-card">
            <div class="value-icon">
                <i class="fas fa-heart"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Quality First</h3>
            <p>We source only the finest fabrics and materials, ensuring each piece not only looks beautiful but stands the test of time.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="value-card">
            <div class="value-icon">
                <i class="fas fa-leaf"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Sustainability</h3>
            <p>We're committed to ethical production practices and sustainable materials, because beautiful fashion should be responsible too.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="value-card">
            <div class="value-icon">
                <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Customer Love</h3>
            <p>Our customers are at the heart of everything we do. Your satisfaction and confidence drive our passion and innovation.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

